<img alt="" width="20" height="20" src="https://leakfree.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/k/a183cd/40.png" class="avatar"> Kazioo:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>True about mod and hugely impressive, but the steam commercial release will be treated like every other commercial game and all the gameplay balancing problems and glitches will be pointed out by reviewers this time.</p>
